title: Find driving schools, lessons and instructors

heading_context: Find driving schools, lessons and instructors
Check a driving instructor who is not listed
chunks.html_content:
Find driving instructors who are approved by the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) and check their grade (if they declare it).

Approved driving instructors (ADIs) choose whether or not to be on this service, so not all ADIs will be listed.

Contact DVSA to check if the driving instructor is qualified.

You need their name and ADI number (if you have it).
